---
import SectionHeader from '../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
import Card from '../ui/Card.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-24 bg-slate-50 border-y border-brand-border/40">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <SectionHeader
      title="We Build Complete Online Learning Systems"
      description="TheEduAssist is built for people and organizations that want to teach, sell, or deliver training online but need help turning scattered knowledge into a professional learning experience."
    />

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMain mb-4">
            We are not only a web design service. We are not only a Kajabi setup service.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMain">
            We help connect course structure, learner experience, platform setup, content assets, funnels, automation, and ongoing support.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <Card className="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-softBlue flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand-primary">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Learning design before decoration</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMuted flex-grow">We focus on pedagogical structure and outcomes before choosing fonts or colors.</p>
      </Card>

      <Card className="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
         <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-softGreen flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand-accent">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Structure before upload</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMuted flex-grow">We organize content into logical modules, lessons, and journeys before building the platform.</p>
      </Card>

      <Card className="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
         <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-softBlue flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand-primary">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Platform setup with learner flow</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMuted flex-grow">We build systems that are intuitive for the student to navigate from purchase to completion.</p>
      </Card>

      <Card className="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
         <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-softGreen flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand-accent">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Launch support beyond the first page</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMuted flex-grow">We connect the funnels, automations, and tracking needed to actually run a learning business.</p>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
